						<summary>

						<p><hi rend="bold">Pārtiva, Āvaṇi 31 = c. 16th century A.D.</hi></p>						

						<p>Some decision made by the Eṟaraṭṭiyār of Pattippūṇḍi who was the headman <hi rend="italic">(maṇiyam)</hi> to fix the rate on betel gardens in Karuvūr at 15 paṇam only. (A second fragment refers to income from the tax <hi rend="italic">vēlipoṉ</hi> collected for the renovation work).</p>						

